{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TLSClientConnectionRef\/onNotifyRequireCloseNotify(flags:handler:)"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyRequireCloseNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO16TLSConnectionRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TLSConnectionRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TLSConnectionRef"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}]}],"name":"flags"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notifyRequireCloseNotify"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}],"name":"handler"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting thi